---
export const prerender = true;

import LandingLayout from '../../../../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';
---

<LandingLayout
  title="Origgo: +107% de receita em 3 meses com CRM · edrone"
  description="Como a Origgo, marca de moda masculina, cresceu 107% em receita e CLV em apenas 3 meses usando CRM e automação de marketing da edrone."
  lang="pt-BR"
  ogTitle="Origgo: +107% de receita em 3 meses com CRM edrone"
  ogDescription="+107% receita. +107% CLV. 30% taxa de recompra. 3 meses. Veja como a estratégia funcionou."
  googleFont="Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@700;800"
  extraGoogleFonts={["Roboto:wght@300;400;500"]}
>

<style>
    :root { --dark: #2D2D29; --turquoise: #40E0D0; --green: #50C878; --pink: #FFD1DC; --off-white: #FAFAF5; --font-head: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', 'Arial Black', sans-serif; --font-body: 'Roboto', sans-serif; }
    body { font-family: var(--font-body); color: var(--dark); background: var(--yellow); overflow-x: hidden; }
    h1, h2, h3 { font-family: var(--font-head); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1; }
    h1 { font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.8rem); } h2 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); } h3 { font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.8vw, 1.5rem); }
    p { font-family: var(--font-body); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.7; }
    .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 28px; } .section { padding: 96px 0; }
    .badge { display: inline-block; font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 100px; border: 1.5px solid currentColor; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease; cursor: pointer; border: none; }
    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .btn-dark { background: var(--dark); color: var(--yellow); } .btn-dark:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(45,45,41,0.28); }
    .btn-yellow { background: var(--yellow); color: var(--dark); } .btn-yellow:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(255,255,140,0.5); }
    header { position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; background: rgba(255,255,140,0.95); border-bottom: 1.5px solid rgba(45,45,41,0.1); backdrop-filter: blur(8px); }
    .nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 28px; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .logo { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--dark); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: -0.03em; }
    .nav-cta { padding: 10px 24px; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    #hero { background: var(--yellow); padding: 72px 0 88px; overflow: hidden; }
    .hero-inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 420px; gap: 64px; align-items: center; }
    .hero-badge { color: var(--dark); opacity: 0.7; }
    .hero-text h1 { color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .hero-text p { font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgba(45,45,41,0.72); max-width: 520px; margin-bottom: 36px; line-height: 1.65; }
    .hero-kpis { display: flex; gap: 36px; margin-top: 28px; padding-top: 28px; border-top: 1.5px solid rgba(45,45,41,0.14); flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .kpi-item strong { display: block; font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--dark); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .kpi-item span { font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(45,45,41,0.55); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
    .crm-dashboard { background: var(--dark); border-radius: 20px; padding: 28px; box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(45,45,41,0.22), 0 6px 16px rgba(45,45,41,0.1); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
    .crm-dashboard::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -60px; right: -60px; width: 200px; height: 200px; border-radius: 50%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(64,224,208,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%); pointer-events: none; }
    .dash-header { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .dash-title { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(255,255,140,0.4); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; }
    .dash-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--green); box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--green); animation: pulse-dot 2s ease-in-out infinite; }
    @keyframes pulse-dot { 0%, 100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0.4; } }
    .dash-metric-big { text-align: center; padding: 24px 0 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,140,0.08); margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .dash-metric-big .dm-num { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 4rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--yellow); line-height: 1; display: block; animation: count-up 1.8s ease-out both; }
    @keyframes count-up { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    .dash-metric-big .dm-lbl { font-size: 0.72rem; color: rgba(255,255,140,0.38); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-top: 6px; display: block; }
    .dash-metrics-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .dash-metric { background: rgba(255,255,140,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,140,0.08); border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px 16px; }
    .dash-metric .dm-val { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--turquoise); display: block; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .dash-metric .dm-name { font-size: 0.68rem; color: rgba(255,255,140,0.35); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
    .dash-channels { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
    .dash-ch-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 72px 1fr 38px; gap: 10px; align-items: center; }
    .dash-ch-name { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(255,255,140,0.55); text-transform: uppercase; }
    .dash-ch-track { height: 6px; background: rgba(255,255,140,0.06); border-radius: 100px; overflow: hidden; }
    .dash-ch-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 100px; animation: grow-bar 1.4s ease-out both; }
    .fill-email { background: var(--yellow); } .fill-sms { background: var(--turquoise); }
    @keyframes grow-bar { from { width: 0%; } }
    .dash-ch-pct { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(255,255,140,0.35); text-align: right; }
    .dash-period { margin-top: 18px; padding-top: 14px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,140,0.06); font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(255,255,140,0.2); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-align: center; }
    #problem { background: var(--off-white); }
    .problem-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 72px; align-items: start; }
    .problem-text h2 { margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .problem-text p { font-size: 1.05rem; color: rgba(45,45,41,0.72); margin-bottom: 32px; line-height: 1.7; }
    .stat-pill { display: inline-flex; flex-direction: column; background: var(--yellow); padding: 20px 28px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1.5px solid rgba(45,45,41,0.12); }
    .stat-pill strong { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .stat-pill span { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(45,45,41,0.6); max-width: 180px; line-height: 1.4; }
    .problem-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; padding-top: 8px; }
    .problem-list li { display: flex; gap: 14px; font-size: 0.97rem; color: rgba(45,45,41,0.78); line-height: 1.6; }
    .picon { flex-shrink: 0; width: 26px; height: 26px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--dark); color: var(--yellow); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2px; }
    .problem-list li strong { color: var(--dark); }
    #solution { background: var(--yellow); } #solution h2 { margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .section-sub { font-size: 1.05rem; color: rgba(45,45,41,0.68); max-width: 580px; margin-bottom: 56px; line-height: 1.7; }
    .flow { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 4px; margin-bottom: 56px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .flow-step { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; text-align: center; gap: 10px; min-width: 90px; padding: 4px; }
    .flow-icon { width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--dark); color: var(--yellow); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.35rem; }
    .flow-step span { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--dark); max-width: 80px; line-height: 1.3; }
    .flow-arrow { font-size: 1.2rem; color: rgba(45,45,41,0.3); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .strategy-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .strategy-card { background: var(--white); border: 1.5px solid rgba(45,45,41,0.1); border-radius: 14px; padding: 28px 24px; transition: transform 0.18s, box-shadow 0.18s; }
    .strategy-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(45,45,41,0.1); }
    .strategy-icon { font-size: 2rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .strategy-label { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .strategy-desc { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(45,45,41,0.6); line-height: 1.6; }
    .setup-note { text-align: center; padding: 20px 0 0; border-top: 1.5px solid rgba(45,45,41,0.12); font-size: 0.88rem; color: rgba(45,45,41,0.6); }
    .setup-note strong { color: var(--dark); }
    #results { background: var(--dark); color: var(--yellow); }
    #results .badge { border-color: rgba(255,255,140,0.25); color: rgba(255,255,140,0.55); }
    .results-hero { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 64px; }
    .big-number { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: clamp(5rem, 15vw, 11rem); font-weight: 800; color: var(--yellow); line-height: 0.9; letter-spacing: -0.04em; display: block; margin: 8px 0 16px; }
    .big-sub { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(255,255,140,0.4); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
    .results-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 52px; }
    .result-card { border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,140,0.12); border-radius: 14px; padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .result-card .rnum { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 2.6rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--yellow); display: block; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .result-card .rlbl { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(255,255,140,0.45); line-height: 1.4; }
    .breakdown { margin-top: 8px; }
    .breakdown-title { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(255,255,140,0.4); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .bar-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 130px 1fr 180px; gap: 16px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .bar-name { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--yellow); }
    .bar-track { height: 8px; background: rgba(255,255,140,0.08); border-radius: 100px; overflow: hidden; }
    .bar-fill { height: 100%; background: var(--turquoise); border-radius: 100px; }
    .bar-val { font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,140,0.5); text-align: right; }
    .results-note { text-align: center; margin-top: 36px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,140,0.28); letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
    #why { background: var(--off-white); } #why h2 { margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .why-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
    .why-card { background: var(--white); border: 1.5px solid rgba(45,45,41,0.07); border-radius: 18px; padding: 36px 32px; transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; }
    .why-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(45,45,41,0.07); }
    .why-num { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 3.2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--yellow); display: block; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .why-card h3 { margin-bottom: 12px; } .why-card p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: rgba(45,45,41,0.68); line-height: 1.7; }
    #testimonial { background: var(--yellow); }
    .testimonials-stack { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 40px; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .testimonial-card { background: var(--white); border-radius: 20px; padding: 40px 44px; position: relative; border: 1.5px solid rgba(45,45,41,0.07); }
    .testimonial-card.founder { background: var(--dark); }
    .quote-glyph { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 5rem; line-height: 0.6; display: block; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .founder .quote-glyph { color: rgba(255,255,140,0.15); } .agency .quote-glyph { color: rgba(45,45,41,0.1); }
    blockquote { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2vw, 1.4rem); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .founder blockquote { color: var(--yellow); } .agency blockquote { color: var(--dark); }
    .author { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; }
    .author-avatar { width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-family: var(--font-head); font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.95rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .founder .author-avatar { background: var(--yellow); color: var(--dark); } .agency .author-avatar { background: var(--dark); color: var(--yellow); }
    .author-info strong { display: block; font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.93rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .founder .author-info strong { color: var(--yellow); } .agency .author-info strong { color: var(--dark); }
    .author-info span { font-size: 0.78rem; }
    .founder .author-info span { color: rgba(255,255,140,0.45); } .agency .author-info span { color: rgba(45,45,41,0.45); }
    .brand-row { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 28px; margin-top: 48px; padding-top: 36px; border-top: 1.5px solid rgba(45,45,41,0.12); flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .brand-chip { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 800; color: rgba(45,45,41,0.38); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
    .brand-sep { width: 1px; height: 20px; background: rgba(45,45,41,0.18); }
    #cta-final { background: var(--dark); text-align: center; }
    #cta-final .badge { border-color: rgba(255,255,140,0.25); color: rgba(255,255,140,0.45); }
    #cta-final h2 { color: var(--yellow); margin-bottom: 14px; }
    #cta-final p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: rgba(255,255,140,0.55); max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto 40px; line-height: 1.7; }
    .proof-row { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 28px; margin-top: 28px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .proof-item { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(255,255,140,0.35); } .proof-dot { width: 4px; height: 4px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(255,255,140,0.18); }
    .cta-micro { display: block; margin-top: 14px; font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(255,255,140,0.28); }
    footer { background: var(--yellow); padding: 36px 28px; border-top: 1.5px solid rgba(45,45,41,0.1); }
    .footer-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px; }
    .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .footer-links a { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(45,45,41,0.5); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.15s; }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--dark); }
    .fade-up { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); transition: opacity 0.65s ease, transform 0.65s ease; }
    .fade-up.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    @media (max-width: 920px) { .hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .crm-dashboard { display: none; } .problem-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; } .strategy-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } .results-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } .why-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .bar-row { grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr 140px; gap: 10px; } }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .section { padding: 64px 0; } .strategy-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 14px; } .results-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .why-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .flow-arrow { display: none; } .big-number { font-size: 5rem; } .bar-row { grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr; } .bar-val { display: none; } .hero-kpis { gap: 20px; } .testimonial-card { padding: 28px 24px; } }
</style>

<header><nav class="nav"><a href="https://edrone.me/br" class="logo">edrone</a><a href="#cta-final" class="btn btn-dark nav-cta">Agendar demo →</a></nav></header>

<section id="hero"><div class="container"><div class="hero-inner">
  <div class="hero-text fade-up">
    <span class="badge hero-badge">Case de Sucesso Real · Moda Masculina · 2024</span>
    <h1>+107% de receita em&nbsp;3&nbsp;meses.<br>Sem mudar o produto.</h1>
    <p>Como a Origgo parou de gastar em tráfego e começou a vender mais para quem já conhecia a marca — usando CRM, automação comportamental e multicanal.</p>
    <a href="#cta-final" class="btn btn-dark">Quero isso na minha loja →</a>
    <div class="hero-kpis">
      <div class="kpi-item"><strong>+107%</strong><span>Crescimento em receita</span></div>
      <div class="kpi-item"><strong>+107%</strong><span>Aumento no CLV</span></div>
      <div class="kpi-item"><strong>30%</strong><span>Taxa de recompra</span></div>
      <div class="kpi-item"><strong>3 meses</strong><span>Com o CRM edrone</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="crm-dashboard">
    <div class="dash-header"><span class="dash-title">Painel CRM · Origgo</span><div class="dash-dot"></div></div>
    <div class="dash-metric-big"><span class="dm-num">+107%</span><span class="dm-lbl">Crescimento de receita vs. período anterior</span></div>
    <div class="dash-metrics-row"><div class="dash-metric"><span class="dm-val">+107%</span><span class="dm-name">CLV por cliente</span></div><div class="dash-metric"><span class="dm-val">30%</span><span class="dm-name">Taxa de recompra</span></div></div>
    <div class="dash-channels">
      <p class="breakdown-title" style="color:rgba(255,255,140,0.28); margin-bottom:12px;">Canais ativos</p>
      <div class="dash-ch-row"><span class="dash-ch-name">E-mail</span><div class="dash-ch-track"><div class="dash-ch-fill fill-email" style="width:78%"></div></div><span class="dash-ch-pct">78%</span></div>
      <div class="dash-ch-row"><span class="dash-ch-name">SMS</span><div class="dash-ch-track"><div class="dash-ch-fill fill-sms" style="width:22%"></div></div><span class="dash-ch-pct">22%</span></div>
    </div>
    <p class="dash-period">Origgo · Moda masculina · Agência Nexgenius · 3 meses</p>
  </div>
</div></div></section>

<section id="problem" class="section"><div class="container"><div class="problem-grid fade-up">
  <div class="problem-text">
    <span class="badge">O Problema</span>
    <h2>Você investe em tráfego. Mas quem compra de novo?</h2>
    <p>A Origgo já tinha um e-mail marketing funcionando — mas sem jornada, sem contexto, sem integração com o comportamento real do cliente. Disparava mensagens. Não construía relacionamento.</p>
    <div class="stat-pill"><strong>5–8×</strong><span>mais caro adquirir um novo cliente do que reativar quem já comprou</span></div>
  </div>
  <ul class="problem-list">
    <li><div class="picon">✗</div><div><strong>E-mail sem comportamento.</strong> Todos recebiam a mesma mensagem, no mesmo momento — independente de onde estavam na jornada de compra.</div></li>
    <li><div class="picon">✗</div><div><strong>Sem visibilidade de impacto.</strong> Não era possível saber se o e-mail realmente influenciava a venda — só que a mensagem havia sido enviada.</div></li>
    <li><div class="picon">✗</div><div><strong>Base subaproveitada.</strong> Clientes que já confiavam na marca não recebiam comunicação relevante. O potencial de recompra era desperdiçado.</div></li>
    <li><div class="picon">✗</div><div><strong>CLV estagnado.</strong> Sem nutrição inteligente, cada venda era tratada como um evento isolado — e não como o início de uma relação lucrativa.</div></li>
  </ul>
</div></div></section>

<section id="solution" class="section"><div class="container fade-up">
  <span class="badge">A Solução</span>
  <h2>CRM + automação comportamental + multicanal.</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">A edrone centralizou os dados de navegação, compra e engajamento da Origgo — e transformou isso em comunicação inteligente, no momento certo, pelo canal certo.</p>
  <div class="flow">
    <div class="flow-step"><div class="flow-icon">📊</div><span>CRM captura dados</span></div><div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
    <div class="flow-step"><div class="flow-icon">🧠</div><span>Segmenta comportamento</span></div><div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
    <div class="flow-step"><div class="flow-icon">⚡</div><span>Automação dispara</span></div><div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
    <div class="flow-step"><div class="flow-icon">📧</div><span>E-mail + SMS</span></div><div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
    <div class="flow-step"><div class="flow-icon">🔁</div><span>Recompra cresce</span></div><div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
    <div class="flow-step"><div class="flow-icon">📈</div><span>CLV dispara</span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="strategy-grid">
